_sText:
::DE_FACTORY V3 FINAL::

Creator = Mark Clark aka Scorchedbee=GCHQ=
Debugging and many fixes/additions Deaths Apprentice=GCHQ=

This is a small map designed so no snipers are really used. There
are a few hiding places and explosive barrels in useful places. The
map is designed around a small factory with 2 offices and a loading
bay, there is also a tunnel and a small rooftop area.

::New in V3::

- Explosive Barrels in usefull areas.
- Dead body in burning truck
- T and CT spawns fixed
- Less dynamic lights for higher FPS
- All bugs fixed
